" Open Design Shared Creativity conference now in its third edition.

Organized by Foment de les Arts i el Disseny (FAD), the conference is part of a great festival (the FADfest precisely) and is accompanied by a great show and many other events: the festival deals with all kind of design approaches and goes far beyond the industrial design that has always seen Barcelona as a protagonist on the international scene."
